data.description: This unique property, with its RV garage, is an adventurer's dream, complemented by a heated in-ground pool for ultimate relaxation and entertainment. Solar power (assumable by the buyer) ensures energy efficiency alongside modern amenities and recent upgrades, including a 2020 pool heater and a 2020 hot water heater. Vaulted ceilings add a touch of elegance to the flexible living spaces, from the formal dining area to the cozy breakfast bar and the adaptable den/flex room Nestled in a community known for its residential allure, this home strikes a perfect balance between serene country living and convenient access to urban amenities. It's a peaceful retreat, yet just a stone's throw from the vibrant Shoppes at Lehigh and within a leisurely 30-mile drive to the sandy shores of Fort Myers Beach. Embrace the lifestyle you've always wanted in this sophisticated, adventure-ready home in South Lehigh Acres, where the tranquility of country living meets the convenience of city proximity. Seize this chance to own a slice of paradise where luxury meets convenience, wrapped in the tranquility of SOUTH LEHIGH ACRES.#SolarHome #RVGarage #HeatedPool #SouthLehighAcresLiving
